948
00:47:26,743 --> 00:47:30,543
Even after prison,
you're kind of still

949
00:47:30,614 --> 00:47:33,674
under prison guidelines,
you know.

950
00:47:35,619 --> 00:47:37,644
WOMAN: Put your right foot
back up, please.

951
00:47:43,060 --> 00:47:45,528
Put that against
your stomach.

952
00:47:47,764 --> 00:47:51,063
ALEXANDER: I refer to the
system of mass incarceration

953
00:47:51,134 --> 00:47:53,398
as a new Jim Crow,

954
00:47:53,470 --> 00:47:57,566
because it is
a comprehensive system

955
00:47:57,641 --> 00:48:01,099
that serves to lock
a group of people,

956
00:48:01,178 --> 00:48:03,578
defined largely
by race and class,

957
00:48:03,647 --> 00:48:07,378
into a permanent
second-class status.

958
00:48:11,255 --> 00:48:15,817
Our racial stereotypes...

959
00:48:15,893 --> 00:48:18,555
fears, and anxieties

960
00:48:18,629 --> 00:48:21,393
have driven the birth
of this system

961
00:48:21,465 --> 00:48:25,765
and sustained the idea
that some people are a problem

962
00:48:25,836 --> 00:48:28,896
to be dealt with harshly.

963
00:48:34,845 --> 00:48:37,575
WOMAN: Sean Bell died
the same day

964
00:48:37,648 --> 00:48:40,617
he was supposed
to get married.

965
00:48:40,684 --> 00:48:42,117
[Gunshot]

966
00:48:42,185 --> 00:48:45,086
MAN: Grant was
fatally wounded.

967
00:48:48,859 --> 00:48:51,293
GATES: As a President
of a nation

968
00:48:51,361 --> 00:48:54,762
eager to disavow
its racial past,

969
00:48:54,831 --> 00:48:57,800
Obama had steered clear
of discussing race

970
00:48:57,868 --> 00:49:00,428
while in the White House.

971
00:49:00,504 --> 00:49:02,631
But during his second term,

972
